50:53.320 --> 50:55.920
Robbie? Come on, have a wee guess.

50:56.920 --> 50:58.760
I was thinking maybe, er...

50:59.520 --> 51:02.760
A Glenfarclas or maybe a Cragganmore.

51:03.000 --> 51:05.560
Well, you know,
that's very interesting because

51:05.760 --> 51:09.160
I was really swithering
between those two myself. Erm...

