51:37.760 --> 51:40.120
Well done. That's great.

51:40.560 --> 51:43.840
In your personal opinion,
not from a book or anything,

51:44.080 --> 51:48.840
what is the finest tasting whisky
in the world that you've ever tasted?

51:49.760 --> 51:52.040
Last night, coincidentally,

51:52.560 --> 51:57.520
