an exchange on marriage

52:41.800 --> 52:45.840
between the manager of the distillery
which made this whisky

52:46.080 --> 52:49.760
and the manager of the distillery
where it was found.

52:50.680 --> 52:52.800
You said it's going
to public auction.

52:53.000 --> 52:56.440
Can you give me an idea... a rough idea
