How in the name of fuck
can we get a donkey away up there?

01:02:53.000 --> 01:02:54.840
- You're a donkey.
- I was just about to say that.

01:02:54.960 --> 01:02:56.640
We're taking a donkey.

01:02:56.800 --> 01:03:01.440
