01:03:29.320 --> 01:03:31.640
We'd just look like friendly wee cunts
up the Highlands.

01:03:31.840 --> 01:03:34.120
Whisky train spotters, know what I mean?

01:03:35.040 --> 01:03:36.920
Albert Einstein.

